(a)        “child” means a person under the age of fourteen years;
(b)        “Controller” means the Controller of Vagrancy, West Pakistan;
(c)        “Government” means the Government of West Pakistan;
(d)        “guardian” in relation to a child, includes any person who in the opinion of the
court having cognizance of any case in which a child is concerned, has for the
